(41, 35, 'Jay Shetty', 'Jay Shetty is a prominent author known for his inspiring and transformative work. Born on September 6, 1987, in London, he began his career as a monk, spending years in India studying ancient philosophies and mindfulness practices. This profound experience laid the foundation for his remarkable insights and teachings.\r\n\r\nWith a passion for personal growth and spiritual wisdom, Jay Shetty transitioned into a successful author and motivational speaker. His best-selling book, \"Think Like a Monk,\" offers practical advice on finding purpose, overcoming challenges, and cultivating a more meaningful life. Jay\'s unique ability to blend ancient wisdom with modern concepts has garnered him a massive global following.\r\n\r\nBeyond his books, Shetty is a sought-after speaker, delivering engaging talks on platforms like TED and YouTube, where his videos have reached millions of viewers. His relatable storytelling and relatable approach make his message accessible to diverse audiences worldwide.\r\n\r\nJay Shetty\'s impact extends beyond literature, as he is deeply involved in philanthropic work, promoting mental health awareness and empowering youth. Through his writing and public speaking, Jay Shetty continues to inspire countless individuals to pursue a path of purpose, positivity, and inner fulfilment.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690884758/Jay_Shetty_Headshot_2021_yd5hr9.jpg'),
(42, 35, 'Ankur Warikoo', 'Ankur Warikoo is a prominent Indian entrepreneur, author, and motivational speaker known for his immense contributions to the start-up ecosystem and personal development space. He co-founded Nearbuy (formerly Groupon India), an online platform offering local deals and experiences. Ankur is highly regarded for his influential talks on various platforms, inspiring countless individuals with his insights and wisdom.\r\n\r\nAs an author, Ankur has penned several books that have resonated with readers globally. His writing delves into themes of self-improvement, entrepreneurship, and leadership, providing practical guidance and inspiration to his audience. His books stand as a testament to his commitment to empowering people to achieve their fullest potential and create a positive impact in the world.\r\n\r\nAn alumnus of the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT), Delhi, and the Indian School of Business (ISB), Ankur possesses a strong academic background in engineering and business management. Through his successful ventures, compelling speeches, and impactful writing, Ankur Warikoo continues to be a guiding force for aspiring entrepreneurs and individuals seeking personal growth and fulfilment.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690884797/X9eoDIB9cgb1s-kvATRs1lQDcU4Fjc15NDV9s9FF8ck7IsA8u7OdijaernoDV9LLdePgjlt__s900-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj_gbex7f.jpg'),
(43, 35, 'Gaur Gopal Das', 'Gaur Gopal Das is a renowned Indian author, motivational speaker, and spiritual leader who has captivated millions with his profound wisdom and engaging storytelling. Born in a Punjabi family, he pursued his education in engineering but later embraced a life of spirituality at the International Society for Krishna Consciousness (ISKCON) in 1996.\r\n\r\nWith his mesmerizing oratory skills, Gaur Gopal Das has inspired countless individuals globally to lead a purposeful life filled with positivity, love, and compassion. He emphasizes the importance of finding inner peace and contentment while navigating the complexities of the modern world.\r\n\r\nGaur Gopal Das is an accomplished author, having penned down several best-selling books, each carrying valuable life lessons, and offering practical guidance on personal growth, relationships, and spirituality. His relatable anecdotes and down-to-earth approach make his teachings accessible to people from all walks of life.\r\n\r\nThrough his talks, books, and social media presence, Gaur Gopal Das continues to touch the hearts of millions, guiding them towards a more fulfilling and meaningful existence. His dedication to spreading joy, happiness, and spiritual wisdom has made him a beloved figure in the realm of self-development and spirituality.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885205/guruspeak-a-one_one_jzss7x.jpg'),
(44, 35, 'Sudha Murty', 'Sudha Murty is an esteemed Indian author, philanthropist, and social worker, widely known for her prolific writing and contributions to society. Born on August 19, 1950, she is the chairperson of Infosys Foundation, a non-profit organization that focuses on supporting various social causes, especially in the fields of education, healthcare, rural development, and the empowerment of women and children.\r\n\r\nA versatile writer, Sudha Murty has authored numerous books, ranging from fiction and children\'s literature to travelogues and inspirational stories. Her writing style is simple, yet impactful, often drawing inspiration from real-life experiences and incidents. Her stories seamlessly blend tradition and modernity, addressing social issues and values while captivating readers with their relatable characters and themes.\r\n\r\nSudha Murty\'s literary work has garnered widespread acclaim, making her one of India\'s most beloved authors. Her books have been translated into several languages and have inspired readers of all ages across the globe. Alongside her writing, her tireless dedication to philanthropy has positively impacted countless lives, making her an exemplary figure admired for her compassion, intellect, and commitment to making the world a better place.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885324/Sudha-Murty_ekohny.jpg'),
(45, 35, 'Colleen Hoover', 'Colleen Hoover is a renowned contemporary fiction author known for her compelling storytelling and emotionally charged novels. Born on December 11, 1979, in Sulphur Springs, Texas, Hoover\'s writing career began in 2012 when she self-published her debut novel, \"Slammed.\" Her works often explore complex relationships, love, heartbreak, and personal growth.\r\n\r\nHoover\'s writing style is characterized by its raw authenticity, which resonates deeply with readers. Her ability to craft relatable characters and thought-provoking plots has earned her widespread popularity and critical acclaim. Some of her most beloved works include \"It Ends with Us,\" \"Confess,\" and \"Ugly Love.\"\r\n\r\nOver the years, Colleen Hoover has amassed a dedicated fan base and has received numerous literary awards and nominations for her contributions to contemporary romance and women\'s fiction genres. Her books consistently top bestseller lists, a testament to her skill in capturing the intricacies of human emotions. As a prominent voice in modern literature, Hoover continues to enchant readers with her evocative storytelling and remains a prominent figure in the world of contemporary fiction.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885362/2-23_20dtw_20colleen_20hoover_bxx2qq.jpg'),
(46, 35, 'Aruna Shaibya', 'Aruna Shaibya, an accomplished author, is a wordsmith whose literary prowess knows no bounds. With an innate ability to intricately weave words, she captivates readers with her evocative storytelling and thought-provoking narratives. Shaibya\'s writing reflects a profound understanding of human emotions and relationships, as she skillfully delves into the depths of the human psyche.\r\n\r\nHer prose is a tapestry of vivid imagery and lyrical language, transporting readers to enchanting realms and making the ordinary appear extraordinary. Through her works, she explores themes ranging from love and loss to identity and societal intricacies, offering readers a mirror to contemplate their own lives.\r\n\r\nShaibya\'s commitment to her craft shines through her meticulous attention to detail and her unwavering dedication to honing her skills. Her literary contributions have garnered critical acclaim, resonating with a diverse audience that is drawn to her unique blend of eloquence and insight. Aruna Shaibya\'s legacy as an author is etched in the hearts and minds of those who have had the privilege of experiencing the world through her eloquent prose.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1691161568/Aruna_Shaibya_nxnmhg.jpg'),
(47, 35, 'Amish Tripathi', 'Amish Tripathi is an acclaimed Indian author known for his captivating works in the realm of mythology and fantasy. Born on October 18, 1974, in Mumbai, India, he pursued a career in finance and held positions with leading organizations before delving into writing. Tripathi\'s breakthrough came with his debut novel, \"The Immortals of Meluha\" (2010), the first in the Shiva Trilogy, which reimagines the Hindu god Shiva as a mortal, making him relatable and endearing to readers.\r\n\r\nHis unique storytelling style weaves together ancient Indian myths and historical events with modern elements, breathing new life into age-old tales. With strong character development and meticulous research, Tripathi\'s works have garnered widespread acclaim, propelling him to the ranks of best-selling authors.\r\n\r\nApart from the Shiva Trilogy, he has authored the Ram Chandra Series and the Indic Chronicles. Tripathi\'s contribution to Indian literature has earned him numerous awards and accolades, inspiring a new generation of readers to rediscover their rich cultural heritage through the lens of fiction.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885473/71615391_ralsfl.jpg'),
(48, 35, 'Mark Manson', 'Mark Manson is a renowned contemporary author celebrated for his refreshing approach to self-help and personal development. Born in 1984, he gained international acclaim through his best-selling book, \"The Subtle Art of Not Giving a F*ck,\" published in 2016. Manson\'s writing is characterized by its candid, no-nonsense style, blending humor, brutal honesty, and profound insights. He challenges conventional wisdom, urging readers to confront uncomfortable truths and embrace life\'s inherent struggles to find true meaning and fulfillment.\r\n\r\nManson\'s unique voice resonates with millions, as he addresses common existential dilemmas and mental health issues with empathy and wit. His focus on prioritizing values, setting healthy boundaries, and letting go of unimportant distractions inspires readers to lead authentic and purpose-driven lives. Beyond his books, Manson maintains a prominent online presence, sharing thought-provoking articles and engaging with his followers. His influence extends well beyond the literary world, making Mark Manson a significant figure in the realm of contemporary self-improvement authors.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885557/Mark-manson-headshot-2018-1_gougmy.jpg'),
(50, 35, 'Chetan Bhagat', 'Chetan Bhagat is a renowned Indian author known for his compelling and relatable storytelling. Born on April 22, 1974, in New Delhi, India, Bhagat pursued a successful career as an investment banker before venturing into writing. He made his literary debut with the best-selling novel \"Five Point Someone\" in 2004, which brought him widespread acclaim and popularity among young readers.\r\n\r\nBhagat\'s writing style is characterized by its simplicity and the ability to address contemporary social issues. His works often revolve around the lives of young individuals facing personal and professional challenges, making his narratives relatable and accessible to a wide audience.\r\n\r\nThroughout his career, Bhagat has authored several other popular novels, including \"One Night @ the Call Center,\" \"2 States,\" \"Revolution 2020,\" and \"Half Girlfriend.\" His books have been adapted into successful Bollywood films and have further cemented his position as one of India\'s most influential contemporary authors.\r\n\r\nChetan Bhagat\'s literary contributions have not only entertained millions but have also sparked important discussions on societal issues, making him a prominent figure in Indian literature.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885615/AOPolaRZDLuN_oaLY4A7KmMtPwwUxNwzsjy7rSHPrV1I_s900-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj_uacqrd.jpg'),
(51, 35, 'Sadhguru', 'Sadhguru, born Jaggi Vasudev, is a prominent Indian yogi, mystic, and spiritual teacher. He is renowned for his profound wisdom, captivating speaking style, and charismatic presence, which have touched the lives of millions worldwide. As the founder of the Isha Foundation, he has dedicated his life to promoting personal growth, well-being, and spiritual transformation.\r\n\r\nSadhguru\'s teachings are rooted in ancient yogic practices and modern insights, emphasizing the importance of inner exploration and self-realization. His messages encompass various aspects of life, including spirituality, health, relationships, and environmental sustainability.\r\n\r\nThrough his popular public talks, online presence, and volunteer-led programs, Sadhguru has become an influential figure, inspiring people to find purpose, live joyfully, and embrace life\'s challenges with equanimity. He has also been actively involved in various social and environmental initiatives, striving to create a positive impact on society and the planet.\r\n\r\nSadhguru\'s ability to blend profound wisdom with a sense of humour and practicality makes him an accessible guide for those seeking spiritual growth and personal transformation. His magnetic persona and commitment to human well-being have earned him a devoted global following.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885646/jBfoRxDyDktypbBYYra8woH5YUM9C89E7bDEE2c6qcEjjbGDRXYJEJZd0oyBpMGalKk5Nz8F6Jo_s900-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj_rty0ff.jpg'),
(52, 35, 'Paulo Coelho', 'Paulo Coelho is a renowned Brazilian author, born on August 24, 1947, in Rio de Janeiro. He is widely celebrated for his captivating storytelling, philosophical insights, and spiritual themes. Coelho\'s literary career began in the 1970s when he published various works, but it was his 1988 novel \"The Alchemist\" that propelled him to international fame and acclaim.\r\n\r\nDrawing inspiration from his own life experiences and spiritual journey, Coelho\'s writings often explore themes of self-discovery, destiny, and the pursuit of dreams. His prose is marked by a unique blend of simplicity and profundity, resonating with readers from diverse backgrounds. Coelho\'s books have been translated into numerous languages, reaching a global audience and selling millions of copies worldwide.\r\n\r\nThroughout his career, Coelho has been recognized with several prestigious literary awards, solidifying his status as one of the most influential authors of his time. His body of work continues to inspire and motivate readers to embrace their true selves, seek their passions, and embark on transformative journeys of self-realization.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885691/ab6761610000e5eb6ad95d8390611f07ff34a0ee_odcx1i.jpg'),
(53, 35, 'Robert T. Kiyosaki', 'Robert T. Kiyosaki is a renowned American author, entrepreneur, and investor, best known for his influential personal finance book \"Rich Dad Poor Dad.\" Born on April 8, 1947, in Hawaii, Kiyosaki\'s work revolves around financial education and building wealth through real estate investments and entrepreneurship.\r\n\r\nIn \"Rich Dad Poor Dad,\" Kiyosaki shares life lessons he learned from his two father figures – his biological father (the \"Poor Dad\") and the father of his best friend (the \"Rich Dad\"). This ground-breaking book challenges conventional beliefs about money, advocating for financial independence and self-reliance. Kiyosaki emphasizes the importance of financial literacy, the power of assets over liabilities, and making informed investment decisions.\r\n\r\nApart from \"Rich Dad Poor Dad,\" Kiyosaki has authored numerous other books, including \"Cashflow Quadrant,\" \"The Business of the 21st Century,\" and \"Rich Dad\'s Guide to Investing,\" all of which further explore his financial principles.\r\n\r\nKiyosaki\'s work has inspired millions worldwide to take control of their financial destinies, encouraging readers to think differently about money, investing, and wealth creation.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885749/robert-office-desk-chewing-glasses-01_bacope.jpg'),
(54, 35, 'Nepoleon Hill', 'Napoleon Hill (1883-1970) was a renowned American author, self-help pioneer, and motivational speaker, widely considered one of the most influential figures in personal development and success literature. He is best known for his ground-breaking book \"Think and Grow Rich,\" published in 1937, which has sold millions of copies worldwide.\r\n\r\nHill\'s life was marked by personal challenges and failures, which fuelled his desire to study successful individuals and understand the principles behind their achievements. He interviewed and studied numerous successful people, including Andrew Carnegie, Thomas Edison, Henry Ford, and Theodore Roosevelt, which formed the basis for his timeless principles on success and achievement.\r\n\r\nIn addition to \"Think and Grow Rich,\" Hill authored several other acclaimed books, focusing on topics such as personal development, positive thinking, and goal-setting. His works continue to inspire and empower people to realize their potential and attain greatness in both personal and professional aspects of life.\r\n\r\nNapoleon Hill\'s legacy endures through his enduring wisdom, motivating readers to adopt a growth mindset and take proactive steps towards their aspirations.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885804/20-Great-Habits-For-A-Positive-Mental-Attitude-Napoleon-Hill_undxry.webp'),
(55, 35, 'Robin Sharma', 'Robin Sharma is a globally acclaimed author known for his impactful works on personal development and leadership. Born in 1964, Sharma hails from Canada and has written numerous bestsellers that have inspired millions worldwide. His most renowned book, \"The Monk Who Sold His Ferrari,\" explores the journey of a successful lawyer who embarks on a transformational quest for happiness and fulfilment.\r\n\r\nDrawing from his background as a leadership expert and motivational speaker, Sharma\'s writing emphasizes the importance of embracing change, seizing opportunities, and cultivating positive habits to achieve success. His engaging and insightful storytelling style resonates with readers of all ages, making his books popular among business leaders, students, and individuals seeking personal growth.\r\n\r\nBeyond his literary contributions, Sharma travels the globe delivering motivational talks and seminars, empowering individuals and organizations to unlock their full potential. With a warm and inspiring presence, Robin Sharma continues to leave a lasting impact on people\'s lives, encouraging them to lead purposeful, successful, and meaningful journeys.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885828/DxgR350GsDpTPiJaBw7VzqOkb0cnVk9NXFj11_0yginziQH8Z9CBY4RiiJ2RH4Zt5iY2-aSXMKQ_s900-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj_b1bnq1.jpg'),
(56, 35, 'Dale Carnegie', 'Dale Carnegie (1888-1955) was an influential American writer, lecturer, and self-improvement expert. He gained worldwide recognition for his ground-breaking work in the field of interpersonal skills and communication. Carnegie\'s most famous book, \"How to Win Friends and Influence People,\" published in 1936, remains one of the best-selling self-help books of all time.\r\n\r\nBorn in Maryville, Missouri, Carnegie\'s early life was marked by financial struggles. However, he went on to attend college and became a successful salesman and public speaker. His passion for understanding human behaviour and improving personal relationships led him to create the Dale Carnegie Training Institute, which offers courses in communication, leadership, and self-confidence.\r\n\r\nCarnegie\'s writing and teachings emphasized the importance of genuine interest in others, active listening, and positive reinforcement to build lasting connections and win people\'s cooperation. His timeless principles have helped millions of individuals enhance their social and professional lives. Dale Carnegie\'s enduring legacy continues to inspire individuals seeking personal and professional growth through improved interpersonal skills and communication abilities.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885845/dale-carnegie-gettyimages-515180032_ajcmbi.jpg'),
(57, 35, 'Rhonda Byrne', 'Rhonda Byrne is a renowned author hailing from Australia, known for her transformative and inspirational works. Born on March 12, 1951, she gained global fame with her best-selling book \"The Secret,\" which was published in 2006. This ground-breaking self-help guide explores the Law of Attraction, emphasizing positive thinking and visualization to manifest desired outcomes.\r\n\r\nByrne\'s writing style is accessible and engaging, resonating with millions of readers worldwide. Her books, including \"The Power\" and \"The Magic,\" further delve into the principles of the Law of Attraction, encouraging individuals to take charge of their lives and attract abundance, joy, and success.\r\n\r\nA firm believer in the power of thoughts and emotions, Byrne\'s philosophy centres on the idea that thoughts shape reality. Through her work, she has inspired countless individuals to embrace a more positive mindset and adopt practices such as gratitude and visualization to manifest their dreams and goals.\r\n\r\nRhonda Byrne\'s impactful contributions to the self-help genre have made her an influential figure in personal development, motivating people to unlock their true potential and live a life of fulfilment and happiness.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885918/rhonda-byrne-signs-copies-of-her-new-book-hero_wdesim.jpg'),
(58, 35, 'Brian Tracy', 'Brian Tracy is a highly acclaimed author, motivational speaker, and success expert known for his influential work in personal and professional development. Born on January 5, 1944, Tracy\'s career spans over four decades, during which he has authored numerous best-selling books that have been translated into multiple languages. His most renowned works include \"Eat That Frog!\" and \"The Psychology of Achievement,\" which have empowered millions to achieve their goals and maximize their potential.\r\n\r\nTracy\'s writing style is engaging, practical, and actionable, providing readers with step-by-step strategies to overcome obstacles, boost productivity, and cultivate a winning mindset. He emphasizes the significance of goal-setting, time management, and continuous learning as essential components for success. With his vast knowledge and expertise in business, sales, and leadership, Brian Tracy has become a trusted authority for individuals and organizations seeking to excel in their pursuits.\r\n\r\nThrough his motivational seminars and training programs, Tracy has inspired countless individuals worldwide to unleash their greatness and take charge of their lives. His enduring legacy lies in his commitment to empowering others with the tools and principles needed to attain personal and professional excellence.', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/bookland/image/upload/v1690885954/2065083_cys60b.jpg'),
